<plot>On the way home from school, Ryan, senses 'something' in the air. When he reaches his house, his stepmother Lisa, calls to ensure that he has arrived home safely and asks him not to open the door to anyone. Ryan promises to do so, but the promise is broken when a mysterious teen, Luci, shows up at his door step. From there on, Ryan is faced with the opposites that exist in the world and the possible creator of it all. Luci demands to play a game in exchange for him leaving Ryan's home. A game that literally takes your soul away.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?346387</url></doc>
